Package: metaoverfit
Type: Package
Title: Optimism-Corrected Heterogeneity in Meta-Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Mahmood", family = "Ahmad", email = "mahmood.ahmad2@nhs.net", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Implements cross-validation methods to detect and correct for overfitting in meta-regression. Provides optimism-corrected R-squared measures, bootstrap confidence intervals, and diagnostic tools for assessing the reliability of heterogeneity explanations in meta-analysis.
